	<p class="image"><a href="../../article/sarah-vine-vitamin-drips-have-kept-me-bug-free.html" title="Sarah Vine: how vitamin drips help keep me bug free"><img src="https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/b9gtglive/public/image/vitamin-injetcion.jpg" alt="Sarah Vine: how vitamin drips help keep me bug free"></a></p>
	<h2><a href="../../article/sarah-vine-vitamin-drips-have-kept-me-bug-free.html" title="Sarah Vine: how vitamin drips help keep me bug free">Sarah Vine: how vitamin drips help keep me bug free</a></h2>

			<ul class="dateAuthor">
			<li class="first">5 hours ago</li>
					</ul>
		<p>Our columnist swaps vitamin pills for a trip to the Elixir Clinic...<br><a class="readMore" href="../../article/sarah-vine-vitamin-drips-have-kept-me-bug-free.html" title="Read more >>>">Read more >>></a></p></div><div class="listing">
	<p class="image"><a href="../../article/sarah-vine-my-energy-levels-have-shot-up-i-m-more-focused-and-far-less-emotional-which-is-a-relief-all-round.html" title="&quot;My energy levels have shot up, I’m more focused and far less emotional, which is a relief all round&quot;"><img src="https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/b9gtglive/public/image/sarah-vine-8.jpg" alt=""My energy levels have shot up, I’m more focused and far less emotional, which is a relief all round""></a></p>
	<h2><a href="../../article/sarah-vine-my-energy-levels-have-shot-up-i-m-more-focused-and-far-less-emotional-which-is-a-relief-all-round.html" title="&quot;My energy levels have shot up, I’m more focused and far less emotional, which is a relief all round&quot;">"My energy levels have shot up, I’m more focused and far less emotional, which is a relief all round"</a></h2>

			<ul class="dateAuthor">
			<li class="first">February 24th 2017</li>
					</ul>
		<p>Sarah Vine feels better approaching 50 and going through the menopause than she did at 40. The reason? A daily testosterone hormone prescription<br><a class="readMore" href="../../article/sarah-vine-my-energy-levels-have-shot-up-i-m-more-focused-and-far-less-emotional-which-is-a-relief-all-round.html" title="Read more >>>">Read more >>></a></p></div><br class="clear"><div class="listing">
	<p class="image"><a href="../../article/sarah-vine-the-days-of-stretch-and-staple-cosmetic-surgery-are-well-and-truly-over.html" title="Sarah Vine: &quot;The days of ‘stretch and staple’ cosmetic surgery are well and truly over&quot;"><img src="https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/b9gtglive/public/image/sarah-vine-main.jpg" alt="Sarah Vine: "The days of ‘stretch and staple’ cosmetic surgery are well and truly over""></a></p>
	<h2><a href="../../article/sarah-vine-the-days-of-stretch-and-staple-cosmetic-surgery-are-well-and-truly-over.html" title="Sarah Vine: &quot;The days of ‘stretch and staple’ cosmetic surgery are well and truly over&quot;">Sarah Vine: "The days of ‘stretch and staple’ cosmetic surgery are well and truly over"</a></h2>

			<ul class="dateAuthor">
			<li class="first">February 13th 2017</li>
					</ul>
		<p>Today's announcement of a 40% drop in cosmetic surgery procedures ushers in a new era of anti-ageing solutions. Good news for women, says Get The Gloss' co-founder Sarah Vine<br><a class="readMore" href="../../article/sarah-vine-the-days-of-stretch-and-staple-cosmetic-surgery-are-well-and-truly-over.html" title="Read more >>>">Read more >>></a></p></div><div class="listing">
	<p class="image"><a href="../../article/sarah-vine-should-we-be-taking-testosterone-for-menopause.html" title="Sarah Vine: should we be taking testosterone for menopause?"><img src="https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/b9gtglive/public/image/sarah-vine-5.jpg" alt="Sarah Vine: should we be taking testosterone for menopause?"></a></p>
	<h2><a href="../../article/sarah-vine-should-we-be-taking-testosterone-for-menopause.html" title="Sarah Vine: should we be taking testosterone for menopause?">Sarah Vine: should we be taking testosterone for menopause?</a></h2>

			<ul class="dateAuthor">
			<li class="first">October 18th 2016</li>
					</ul>
		<p>A leading gynaecologist is calling for testosterone to be given to menopausal women; why not, if it boosts energy, libido and bone density  - and combats middle-aged spread? Sarah Vine books an appointment<br><a class="readMore" href="../../article/sarah-vine-should-we-be-taking-testosterone-for-menopause.html" title="Read more >>>">Read more >>></a></p></div><br class="clear"><div class="listing">
	<p class="image"><a href="../../article/the-exercise-regime-sarah-vine-swears-by.html" title="Sarah Vine: The expensive exercise regime that really works"><img src="https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/b9gtglive/public/image/library-gym.jpg" alt="Sarah Vine: The expensive exercise regime that really works"></a></p>
	<h2><a href="../../article/the-exercise-regime-sarah-vine-swears-by.html" title="Sarah Vine: The expensive exercise regime that really works">Sarah Vine: The expensive exercise regime that really works</a></h2>

			<ul class="dateAuthor">
			<li class="first">June 17th 2016</li>
					</ul>
		<p>After years of trying and failing with various new workout plans, Sarah Vine has finally found 'the one' - and what's more, she's sticking with it<br><a class="readMore" href="../../article/the-exercise-regime-sarah-vine-swears-by.html" title="Read more >>>">Read more >>></a></p></div><div class="listing">
	<p class="image"><a href="../../article/sarah-vine-why-do-we-fear-the-m-word.html" title="Sarah Vine: why do we still fear the M-word?"><img src="https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/b9gtglive/public/image/menopause-4.jpg" alt="Sarah Vine: why do we still fear the M-word?"></a></p>
	<h2><a href="../../article/sarah-vine-why-do-we-fear-the-m-word.html" title="Sarah Vine: why do we still fear the M-word?">Sarah Vine: why do we still fear the M-word?</a></h2>

			<ul class="dateAuthor">
			<li class="first">June 12th 2016</li>
					</ul>
		<p>When so many expressions of sexuality are now accepted by society, why are we made to feel embarrassed about being menopausal?<br><a class="readMore" href="../../article/sarah-vine-why-do-we-fear-the-m-word.html" title="Read more >>>">Read more >>></a></p></div><br class="clear"><div class="listing">
