	<p class="image"><a href="../../article/sarah-vine-proof-that-the-high-fat-diet-works.html" title="Sarah Vine: Proof that the high fat diet works"><img src="https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/b9gtglive/public/image/gtg-sarah-vine-high-fat-diet-main-1.jpg" alt="Sarah Vine: Proof that the high fat diet works"></a></p>
