			<ul class="dateAuthor">
			<li class="first">May 23rd 2016</li>
					</ul>
		<p>Is fat friend or foe when it comes to weight loss? As the debate ignites again, Sarah Vine reveals how she lost half a stone in 10 days on a high fat diet<br><a class="readMore" href="../../article/sarah-vine-proof-that-the-high-fat-diet-works.html" title="Read more >>>">Read more >>></a></p></div><div class="listing">
